python3-hglib
=============
Python3-hglib is a port to support on Python 3.4.

There are surely bugs, but it does pass all unit tests (on OSX)
Whether you should trust them after my port (they changed too) is up for debate.

python-hglib
============

python-hglib is a library with a fast, convenient interface to Mercurial.
It uses Mercurial's command server for communication with hg.

Installation is standard:

  $ python setup.py install

